CustomField.description: This field will set a value of "Booked" or "Not Booked" based on whether a prospect books a meeting via an Inbound Router. The "Not Booked" value will write once the timeout expires within "Queues for prospects who didn't take action". If that timeout expires and someone still books, the value will be overwritten when the booking happens.
CustomField.label: Most Recent Booking Status CP
